-1 MOBILES 'MOBILE TRACK' 'MOBILES TRACK'~
.
	When you attack a mobile, the relation between you and the mobile
won't be the same, until the reboot comes. Before you quit the mobile
will try to track and find you. If it finds you, it will attack directly
to you. If you quit, the mobile will go back to its original place and
wait there. If you go the room of the mobile, the mobile will remember you
and attack you.

