	This spell allows caster to control the death bodies. Since the death
bodies are controlled by the caster, the power of the death body is as powerful
as the caster's.

~

-1 'SUMMON SHADOW'~
Syntax: cast 'summon shadow'

	This spell allows caster to call shadows from the parallel planes. The
shadow arrives as under control of the caster.

~

