	This spell is can only be used by immortals. It is way of punishment.
When this spell is cast, the victim forgets the half of his/her skills and
spells permanantly.

~

-1 'BLADE BARRIER'~
Syntax: cast 'blade barrier' <victim>

	When the caster casts this spell, very sharp blades appear around
the caster and crashes to the victim's body. There is a possibility that
all appeared blades may crash the victim.

